Pre-Game Insights: Netherlands beat South Africa in their previous two World Cup meetings but have not won any matches against them outside of those two.
Ottneil Baartman is the leading South African wicket-taker in T20s this year and the sixth-highest overall.
Max O'Dowd has the highest career strike rate in the Dutch squad at 121.13.
Heinrich Klaasen is not hiding away from the fact that South Africa have unfinished business against the Dutch.
Scott Edwards isn't worried about the nature of the New York pitch and believes in adapting to whatever the wicket brings.
